import React from 'react'
import { AppBar, Container, Toolbar, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Appbar color='transparent' position='static'>
      <Container>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography>Crypto Pedia</Typography>
        </Toolbar>
      </Container>
    </Appbar>
  )
}

export default Header
